txt.en: Lorndúr can be found in Loeglond.\n\nYou should talk to Lorndúr.
River nets can be found along the Forest River between Loeglond and Felegoth.\n\nYou should destroy river nets.

'Shipments from Felegoth have not been making it to Loeglond. I believe someone may be stealing them out of the Forest River before they reach us. Can I ask you to investigate? Travel along the Forest River from here to Felegoth and see what you find.'
Shipments from Felegoth have not been making their way down the Forest River to Loeglond. Lorndúr believes someone is stealing them and would like you to investigate.

Lorndúr listens as you describe the nets you found along the river.\n\n'Those do not sound like the crude nets I would expect Orcs to make, [placeholder]. Someone else is behind this. Thank you for allowing trade to continue to flow down the river.'
